<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:10:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列战争第 300 天：以色列呼吁公民在国外谨慎行事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-300-israel-calls-on-citizens-to-exercise-caution-abroad/00000191-0ed4-d782-af93-1fdc9f490001</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列已做好应对任何情况的准备，并将与美国总统拜登进行对话 ■ 西方外交官警告称，贝鲁特和德黑兰发生暗杀事件后，战争风险有所增加 ■ 真主党领袖纳斯鲁拉：“我们在所有领域都进入了一个新阶段” ■ 以色列证实，哈马斯军事首领穆罕默德·德伊夫 (Mohammed Deif) 在 7 月以色列国防军对汗尤尼斯 (Khan Yunis) 的袭击中丧生 ■ 以下是战争 300 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 16:51:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-300-israel-calls-on-citizens-to-exercise-caution-abroad/00000191-0ed4-d782-af93-1fdc9f490001</guid></item><item><title>《纽约时报》报道称，哈马斯领导人哈尼亚被德黑兰宾馆安置的炸弹炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-haniyeh-killed-by-bomb-planted-in-tehran-guesthouse-nyt-report-says/00000191-0e65-d782-af93-1ffd4fcc0000</link><description>该报告与早前关于这位政治领袖在一次有针对性的空袭中丧生的猜测相矛盾。伊朗官员称这次暗杀是伊朗情报和安全方面的灾难性失败，也是革命卫队的重大尴尬</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:54:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-haniyeh-killed-by-bomb-planted-in-tehran-guesthouse-nyt-report-says/00000191-0e65-d782-af93-1ffd4fcc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列是否故意挑起冲突升级，从而可能将美国拖入冲突？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/is-israel-deliberately-provoking-escalation-that-might-drag-the-u-s-into-the-conflict/00000191-0e5d-dc54-a7dd-ffdfbb610000</link><description>本周在贝鲁特和德黑兰发生的定点杀戮引发了三个基本问题，其中最大的一个是：谁在扩大的地区战争中拥有既得利益？</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:50:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/is-israel-deliberately-provoking-escalation-that-might-drag-the-u-s-into-the-conflict/00000191-0e5d-dc54-a7dd-ffdfbb610000</guid></item><item><title>“世俗的人以更复杂的方式应对生活。宗教提供了解决方案，但它们并不真实”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-01/ty-article/.highlight/secular-people-cope-with-life-in-a-far-more-complex-way/00000191-0e84-dc54-a7dd-ffc6ddc70000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名以色列人在抛开宗教信仰后开始潜水，而一名美国数字游牧者开始想家</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-01/ty-article/.highlight/secular-people-cope-with-life-in-a-far-more-complex-way/00000191-0e84-dc54-a7dd-ffc6ddc70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列柔道运动员彼得·帕奇克（Peter Paltchik）获得铜牌，因巴尔·拉尼尔（Inbar Lanir）获得银牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-clinches-its-first-medal-in-2024-olympics/00000191-0e79-d4cf-afb5-4efd11bb0000</link><description>因巴尔·拉尼尔晋级女子柔道决赛，确保以色列夺得金牌或银牌</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-clinches-its-first-medal-in-2024-olympics/00000191-0e79-d4cf-afb5-4efd11bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长正在考虑对闯入斯德·泰曼基地的 MK 提起诉讼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-mulls-possible-indictments-against-mks-who-broke-into-sde-teiman-base/00000191-0d95-d116-a5d9-0ffdaaa30000</link><description>工党议员 Efrat Reiten 在向总检察长提出的上诉中表示，Zvi Succot 和 Nissim Vaturi 未经授权进入军事基地是严重犯罪行为，不属于议会豁免权范围。法律专家解释原因</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 13:44:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-mulls-possible-indictments-against-mks-who-broke-into-sde-teiman-base/00000191-0d95-d116-a5d9-0ffdaaa30000</guid></item><item><title>愤怒、震惊和怀疑：阿拉伯世界对哈尼亚在德黑兰遇刺事件的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/anger-shock-and-suspicion-arab-world-reacts-to-haniyehs-assassination-in-tehran/00000191-0d6a-dc54-a7dd-ffea7b970000</link><description>虽然一名伊朗记者称伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚 (Ismail Haniyeh) 被杀比 2020 年卡西姆·苏莱马尼 (Qassem Soleimani) 将军的死更为严重，但一些人将指责的矛头指向伊斯兰共和国和以色列</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 13:33:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/anger-shock-and-suspicion-arab-world-reacts-to-haniyehs-assassination-in-tehran/00000191-0d6a-dc54-a7dd-ffea7b970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列证实，哈马斯军事首领、10 月 7 日建筑师穆罕默德·德伊夫 (Mohammed Deif) 在上个月加沙袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-confirms-it-killed-hamas-military-chief-mohammed-deif-in-gaza-strike-in-july/00000191-0d33-dba6-a59d-0f7ba0d40000</link><description>以色列国防军和辛贝特的一份联合声明称，德伊夫在上个月对汗尤尼斯大院的一次袭击中身亡，并杀死了其他哈马斯成员。加沙医疗消息人士报告称，另有约 90 人在袭击中丧生</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 12:22:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-confirms-it-killed-hamas-military-chief-mohammed-deif-in-gaza-strike-in-july/00000191-0d33-dba6-a59d-0f7ba0d40000</guid></item><item><title>由于安全局势，汉莎航空取消 8 月 8 日之前飞往以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/lufthansa-cancels-flights-to-israel-until-august-8-due-to-security-situation/00000191-0db5-dc1a-a3dd-2dffe8750000</link><description>周三，搭乘慕尼黑-特拉维夫经拉纳卡航班的乘客因转机航班取消，不得不留在塞浦路斯等待返回以色列的航班；汉莎航空飞往贝鲁特的航班取消至 8 月 12 日</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 11:59:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/lufthansa-cancels-flights-to-israel-until-august-8-due-to-security-situation/00000191-0db5-dc1a-a3dd-2dffe8750000</guid></item><item><title>实时假新闻：以色列 Telegram 频道如何接管新闻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fake-news-in-real-time-how-israeli-telegram-channels-took-over-the-news/00000191-090f-d4cf-afb5-4ddfc89c0000</link><description>自加沙战争爆发以来，在线团体比电视新闻更快，比报纸影响力更大，在以色列已经获得了数十万追随者</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:34:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fake-news-in-real-time-how-israeli-telegram-channels-took-over-the-news/00000191-090f-d4cf-afb5-4ddfc89c0000</guid></item><item><title>“国际机构对以色列的压力产生了影响。高等法院法官现在听我们的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/pressure-from-international-bodies-has-an-effect-high-court-judges-listen-to-us-now/00000191-09bc-daf5-a7db-effccfae0000</link><description>二十一个以色列非政府组织最近发布了第二份“占领状况”报告——这份令人痛心的报告将加沙战争、西岸定居者暴力以及以色列公民自由的恶化联系在一起。人权医生组织的盖伊·沙莱夫表示，报告中的哈马斯大屠杀不应该被用来压制对以色列暴行的批评</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:46:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/pressure-from-international-bodies-has-an-effect-high-court-judges-listen-to-us-now/00000191-09bc-daf5-a7db-effccfae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军将哈马斯恐怖分子送回军事基地，据称以色列士兵在那里虐待他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-sends-hamas-terrorist-back-to-army-base-where-israeli-soldiers-allegedly-abused-him/00000191-0b08-de2c-a7ff-4f29ca4e0000</link><description>这名被拘留者已被转移到斯德泰曼的野战医院，涉嫌虐待他的士兵的同事仍在医院服役，其中一些人参加了要求释放的示威活动。以色列国防军表示，出于安全原因，不会透露被拘留者的位置信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 03:05:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-sends-hamas-terrorist-back-to-army-base-where-israeli-soldiers-allegedly-abused-him/00000191-0b08-de2c-a7ff-4f29ca4e0000</guid></item><item><title>一场暗杀的余兴节目，而不是以色列与哈马斯的人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/an-assassination-sideshow-instead-of-an-israel-hamas-hostage-deal/00000191-0a75-d4cf-afb5-4ef5ab250000</link><description>伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚周三在德黑兰被杀后的一个大问题是，他的死将如何影响以色列和哈马斯之间的人质谈判</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 03:03:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/an-assassination-sideshow-instead-of-an-israel-hamas-hostage-deal/00000191-0a75-d4cf-afb5-4ef5ab250000</guid></item><item><title>西方调解人担心最近的暗杀行动会增加以色列与真主党和伊朗发生战争的风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/western-mediators-fear-latest-assassinations-raise-risk-of-israel-war-with-hezbollah-iran/00000191-0adf-d4cf-afb5-4edf47740000</link><description>美国驳斥了以色列军队与真主党发生“短暂但激烈”冲突的想法，尤其担心长期战争</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 03:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/western-mediators-fear-latest-assassinations-raise-risk-of-israel-war-with-hezbollah-iran/00000191-0adf-d4cf-afb5-4edf47740000</guid></item><item><title>自 10 月 7 日以来，内塔尼亚胡从未如此受欢迎。他计划充分利用这一优势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-hasnt-been-this-popular-since-october-7-he-plans-on-taking-full-advantage/00000191-0af0-dc54-a7dd-fff23bd20000</link><description>以色列总理站在人民面前，承担起责任 — — 但仅限于贝鲁特暗杀 — — 因为毕竟，成功只有一个父亲 ■ 关键问题是内塔尼亚胡是否会停止破坏人质协议，还是继续受到远方的勒索正确的</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 03:02:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-hasnt-been-this-popular-since-october-7-he-plans-on-taking-full-advantage/00000191-0af0-dc54-a7dd-fff23bd20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列冒着高风险扰乱伊朗及其代理人，离地区战争越来越近</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-must-be-ready-for-all-out-conflagration-after-killing-of-hamas-hezbollah-leaders/00000191-0a35-d833-ab9f-cb37c3a40000</link><description>以色列显然已经准备好冒险，以打破与伊朗及其代理人的消耗循环。问题是，火势的高度很难控制，尤其是当火势有升级的趋势时。事实上，伊朗现在也处于寻求报复的境地，这将使平静变得更加难以实现</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 03:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-must-be-ready-for-all-out-conflagration-after-killing-of-hamas-hezbollah-leaders/00000191-0a35-d833-ab9f-cb37c3a40000</guid></item><item><title>真主党纳斯鲁拉：冲突进入新阶段；内塔尼亚胡和拜登将于周四发表讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-live/irans-leader-reportedly-orders-direct-attack-on-israel-in-response-to-haniyehs-killing/00000191-0b96-dc1a-a1b7-1bfe53f00000</link><description>以色列证实，哈马斯军事首长 10 月 7 日建筑师穆罕默德·德伊夫在上个月加沙袭击中身亡 ■ 以色列国防部长称暗杀德伊夫是根除哈马斯的关键一步 ■ 消息人士称，伊朗及其代理人将开会讨论对以色列的报复 ■据报道，以色列国防军袭击了黎巴嫩南部的目标 ■ 由于担心全面战争迫在眉睫，人质家人在以色列各地开始了抗议活动</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:45:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-live/irans-leader-reportedly-orders-direct-attack-on-israel-in-response-to-haniyehs-killing/00000191-0b96-dc1a-a1b7-1bfe53f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院：即使在战争期间，以色列国防军也必须保护巴勒斯坦人免受约旦河西岸定居者的侵害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-idf-must-protect-palestinians-from-west-bank-settlers-even-during-war/00000191-0a36-dc1a-a1b7-1bfea11d0000</link><description>高等法院针对西岸巴勒斯坦居民提出的请愿作出裁决，他们声称他们没有得到来自暴力犹太定居者的安全保护</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 20:26:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-idf-must-protect-palestinians-from-west-bank-settlers-even-during-war/00000191-0a36-dc1a-a1b7-1bfea11d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列准备应对伊朗对定点清除的多线反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-prepares-for-irans-multi-front-response-to-targeted-killings/00000191-09c1-d833-ab9f-cbe39eaa0000</link><description>随着以色列国防军增加在约旦河西岸的部署，以色列最高级国防官员对真主党和伊朗的预期反应感到左右为难。与此同时，以色列北部社区处于高度戒备状态</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:40:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-prepares-for-irans-multi-front-response-to-targeted-killings/00000191-09c1-d833-ab9f-cbe39eaa0000</guid></item><item><title>神圣化死亡：以色列人为何庆祝暗杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/sanctifying-death-why-israelis-celebrate-assassinations/00000191-0976-daf5-a7db-eff6a53b0000</link><description>“犹太力量”是极右翼国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔领导的奥兹玛·耶胡迪特党的直译，它正在影响这场战争。以色列已成为纵火狂的俄罗斯套娃</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/sanctifying-death-why-israelis-celebrate-assassinations/00000191-0976-daf5-a7db-eff6a53b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>